People ex rel. John A. Roebling’s Sons Co. v. Wemple, Comptroller. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 14, 1892.) Action by the People ex rel. John A. Roebling’s Sons Co. against Edward Wemple, comptroller.

Argued before Mayham, P. J., and Putnam and Herrick, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to resettle order granted. See 18 N. Y. Supp. 504.
